  <walkingGeneralDescription><![CDATA[<p>On an Inghams walking holiday, you have the freedom to explore the area at your own pace. Each day, a new adventure, with as much or as little walking as you like.</p>
<h3>Why we love walking holidays in Saas Fee</h3>
<p>The walking opportunities in this region are superb, Saas Fee offers over 350km of well-marked paths, the majority of which are above the tree line. PostBus services offer access into the valley, and the cable cars and gondolas take walkers to the higher trails and viewpoints. The terrain here is suited to all levels, and there are plenty of family friendly trails too.</p>]]></walkingGeneralDescription>
